rhaps it had a very little more depth than other Bollywood movies that I have seen , but not much at all . I spent more time laughing at the stupidity of the movie than the parts that were supposed to be funny . I did n't shed a single tear nor did I feel like it , rather I was overwhelmed with a feeling of disgust at the attempt at a dramatic ending . I do n't recommend this movie if you want to watch something good , I recommend it if you want to watch a Bollywood movie that is kind of sad .
