0 Here 's an interesting little movie that strictly gives the phrase " low budget " a horrible name . Our physics teacher who has about nine kids creates a strange serum that causes " molecular reorganization " . Students are hopelessly killed from fake coincidences of submarine sandwiches and flying school supplies . Sounds like a resurrection of classic B - movies from the 50s , right ? Nope ! It 's not an example of high camp fun , which is way , WAY off the mark . A glamorous showcase of breasts and butts ensues our desire for pleasure , opposing the horror that should have had 99.44 % more in the first place . Bottom - of - the - barrel entertainment at its best , aided by pints of red blood and dead student bodies . Atrocious movies like this would make the ultimately catastrophic GURU THE MAD MONK ( 1970 ) the work of an intelligent genius who has a Master 's degree in film production ! It 's an automatic " F " , so rest easy !
